    v2 = tmp
    v2 = wp.sin(((tmp + 0.46 / tmp + 0.47) * (v1 + 0.72 / v1 + 0.42)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(0.39) / (wp.abs(v1 + 0.25) / (v2 + 0.47 + v0 + 0.77)))
